WEBVTT

00:02:56.950 --> 00:03:01.006
na kutoa tiba mahsusi kwa kulenga
mabadiliko

00:03:01.950 --> 00:03:04.403
Na matokeo ni karibia muujiza.

00:03:04.427 --> 00:03:06.873
Uvimbe ulionekana kuyeyuka kabisa.

00:03:07.910 --> 00:03:10.422
Bahati mbaya huu sio mwisho
wa hadithi.

00:03:11.077 --> 00:03:13.556
Miezi michache baadae, hii picha ilipigwa.

00:03:14.157 --> 00:03:15.644
Uvimbe umerudi tena.

00:03:16.627 --> 00:03:18.207
Swali ni: Kwanini?

00:03:18.892 --> 00:03:21.324
Jibu ni uvimbe mbalimbali

00:03:22.107 --> 00:03:23.356
Ngoja nifafanue zaidi.

00:03:25.124 --> 00:03:28.612
Hata saratani ndogo kiasi cha
sentimita moja katika mduara

00:03:28.636 --> 00:03:31.329
huhifadhi seli zaidi ya
milioni mia moja tofauti.